arvel/2019/12/20/marvel-what-if-episode-count-more-episodes-other-marvel-studios-disney-plus-series/|title=Kevin Feige Reveals What If\u2026? Has More Episodes Than Marvel Studios' Other Disney+ Series|last=Bonomolo|first=Cameron|website=Comicbook.com|date=December 19, 2019|accessdate=December 20, 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191220170031/https://comicbook.com/marvel/2019/12/20/marvel-what-if-episode-count-more-episodes-other-marvel-studios-disney-plus-series/|archivedate=December 20, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Squeeze\">{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2020/tv/global/marvel-studio-squeeze-animation-what-if-disney-plus-1203529250/|title=Marvel Picks Quebec's Squeeze for Disney Plus Animated Series 'What If\u2026?' (Exclusive)|last=Dams|first=Tim|work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|date=March 10, 2020|accessdate=March 12, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200311174025/https://variety.com/2020/tv/global/marvel-studio-squeeze-animation-what-if-disney-plus-1203529250/|archivedate=March 11, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"PhaseFour\">{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/marvel-unveils-post-avengers-endgame-plans-at-comic-con-1225869|title=Marvel Unveils Post-'Endgame' Slate with 'Eternals', 'Shang-Chi' and Multiple Sequels|last=Couch|first=Aaron|last2=Kit|first2=Borys|work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=July 20, 2019|accessdate=July 20, 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721025858/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/marvel-unveils-post-avengers-endgame-plans-at-comic-con-1225869|archivedate=July 20, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"FranckNewsarama\">{{cite web|url=https://www.newsarama.com/49833-work-on-marvel-studios-what-if-for-disney+-continues-remotely-during-coronavirus-pandemic.html|title=Work on Marvel Studios' What If...? Continues During Coronavirus Pandemic|last=Arrant|first=Chris|work=[[Newsarama]]|date=April 15, 2020|accessdate=April 17, 202