ies/|archive-date=September 11, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Strange\">{{cite web|url=https://www.slashfilm.com/loki-doctor-strange/|title=Marvel's 'Loki' TV Show Will Tie Into 'Doctor Strange 2'; 'Hawkeye' Was Initially Planned as a Movie|last=Pearson|first=Ben|website=[[/Film]]|date=November 7, 2019|access-date=November 7, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107184553/https://www.slashfilm.com/loki-doctor-strange/|archive-date=November 7, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ExpandingUniverse\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.marvel.com/articles/tv-shows/marvel-cinematic-universe-after-avengers-endgame |title=What's Next for the Marvel Cinematic Universe After 'Avengers: Endgame' |last=Dinh |first=Christine |date=November 13, 2019 |website=[[Marvel Entertainment|Marvel.com]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191114091331/https://www.marvel.com/articles/tv-shows/marvel-cinematic-universe-after-avengers-endgame |archive-date=November 14, 2019 |access-date=November 14, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Martino\">{{Cite web |url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/loki-sophia-di-martino-tom-hiddleston-marvel-1203406777/ |title='Loki': Sophia Di Martino to Co-Star With Tom Hiddleston in Marvel Series (Exclusive) |last=Kroll |first=Justin |date=November 15, 2019 |work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191116001134/https://variety.com/2019/film/news/loki-sophia-di-martino-tom-hiddleston-marvel-1203406777/ |archive-date=November 16, 2019 |access-date=November 16, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Martino2\">{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/11/loki-sophia-di-martino-cast-tom-hiddleston-marvel-limited-series-disney-1202787710/ |title='Loki': Sophia Di Martino Joins Tom Hiddleston in Marvel Limited Series For Disney+ |last1=Andreeva |first1=Nellie |last2=Boucher |first2=Geoff |date=November 15, 2019 |work=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |url-status=live |archive-url= |archiv